# 📊 Week 3 – Interactive Sales Dashboard

## 📌 Overview
This project was developed as part of the **Vortex Tech Data Science Internship – Week 3**. It is an interactive sales dashboard built using **Streamlit**, allowing users to upload any CSV dataset and perform basic exploratory data analysis (EDA) through an easy-to-use web interface.

## 🚀 Features
- Upload CSV files
- Preview uploaded dataset
- Display dataset metrics (Rows & Columns)
- Interactive Bar Chart
- Interactive Scatter Plot
- Summary Statistics
- User-friendly Streamlit interface

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- Matplotlib

